title: Coronavirus: Sputnik V vaccine rushed out to wary Russians
title_page: Coronavirus: Sputnik V vaccine rushed out to wary Russians - BBC News
maintext: In a sense, this is no "launch" at all. Russian health workers have been getting vaccinated in tandem with the official trials for several months. Teachers have been eligible too, and VIPs including President Putin's own daughter have had the jab. The list is said to total more than 100,000 people.
